name: Celebration Pinata Cake
description:
So grateful to make a lot of friends on our social media. In the St. Patrick’s Day vibes, we baked this special cake that consisted of Ireland’s chocolate stout cakes and coated with green velvet glaze. It is decorated with heavenly smooth cream with a half-round rainbow waffle on the top.
 
When you slice it, the chocolate “tezos” coins will come out and clatter. It doesn’t stop with that, we complete the cake with St. Patrick’s signature: shamrock, Guinness beer, Leprechaun Hat, and bucket cookies.

We serve 100 whole cakes today. The rest will be burned in several days. So grab them fast!
